            {
              "kind": "plain",
              "text": "٢٠٥. وَقَالَ (عليه ‏السلام): كُلُّ وِعَاءٍ يَضِيقُ بِمَا جُعِلَ فِي"
            }
          ]
        },
        "part_type": "Hadith",
        "path": "/books/nahj-al-balagha:3:128:1",
        "source_url": "https://thaqalayn.net/hadith/32/3/205/253",
        "text": [
          "هِ إِلَّا وِعَاءَ الْعِلْمِ، فَإِنَّهُ يَتَّسِعُ بِهِ."
        ],
        "translations": {
          "en.sayed-ali-raza": [
            "205. Amīr al-mu’minīn, peace be upon him, said: Every container gets narrower according to what is placed in it except the container of knowledge which expands instead."
          ]
        }
      }
